import {
  Box,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemButton,
  ListItemText,
  Divider,
  Drawer,
  ListItemIcon,
} from "@mui/material";
import InboxIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Inbox";
import MailIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Mail";
import HomeIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Home";
import InfoIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Info";
import FavoriteIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Favorite";
import AccountBoxIcon from "@mui/icons-material/AccountBox";
import DeveloperModeIcon from "@mui/icons-material/DeveloperMode";
import { useState, Fragment } from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; // Import the Link component
import { useSelector } from "react-redux";

const LeftDrawerComponent = ({ isOpen, onCloseDrawer }) => {
  console.log("Rendering LeftDrawerComponent");
  const loggedIn = useSelector((bigPie) => bigPie.authSlice.loggedIn);
  console.log("loggedIn:", loggedIn);
  const isBusiness = useSelector((bigPie) => bigPie.authSlice.isBusiness);
  console.log("isBusiness:", isBusiness);
  const isAdmin = useSelector((bigPie) => bigPie.authSlice.isAdmin);
  console.log("isAdmin:", isAdmin);
  const [value, setValue] = useState(0);

  const list = () => (
    <Box
      sx={{ width: { auto: 250 } }}
      role="presentation"
      onClick={onCloseDrawer}
      onKeyDown={onCloseDrawer}
    >
      <List>
        {loggedIn && (
          <>
            <ListItem key="home" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <HomeIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Home" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="about" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/about">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <InfoIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="About" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="favorite" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/favoriteCardPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <FavoriteIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Favorite Cards" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
          </>
        )}
      </List>

      <Divider />
      <List>
        {isBusiness && (
          <>
            <ListItem key="about-business" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/about">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <InfoIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="About" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="favorite-business" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/favoriteCardPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <FavoriteIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Favorite Card" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="my-cards-business" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/mMyCardsPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <AccountBoxIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="My Cards" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
          </>
        )}
      </List>

      <Divider />
      <List>
        {isAdmin && (
          <>
            <ListItem key="home-admin" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <HomeIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Home" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="about-admin" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/about">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <InfoIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="About" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="favorite-admin" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/favoriteCardPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <FavoriteIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Favorite Cards" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="my-cards-admin" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/MyCardsPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <AccountBoxIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="My Cards" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
            <ListItem key="sandbox" disablePadding>
              <ListItemButton component={Link} to="/sandboxPage">
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <DeveloperModeIcon />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary="Sandbox" />
              </ListItemButton>
            </ListItem>
          </>
        )}
      </List>
    </Box>
  );
  return (
    <Drawer anchor="left" open={isOpen} onClose={onCloseDrawer}>
      {list()}
    </Drawer>
  );
};

export default LeftDrawerComponent;
